<div class="content-h1"><h1>《一个数学家的辩白》</h1></div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="place">
<p id="openCatp" style="display:none">开放分类：<a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E4%B9%A6%E7%B1%8D/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="书籍">书籍</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E4%BC%A0%E5%AA%92/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="传媒">传媒</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="出版">出版</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E4%B8%9A/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="出版业">出版业</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E7%89%A9/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="出版物">出版物</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%A6/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="图书">图书</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="数学">数学</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="文化">文化</a></p>
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="information" id="unifyprompt"><div class="summary" id="anchor" name="anchor"><p>《<a href="http://www.baike.com/wiki/%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA" target="_blank">一个</a>数学家的辩白》是一篇由英国数学家G·H·哈代在1940年写成的文章，于当年11月首次出版。</p><span><a action="editsummaryhref" href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="editSummary();return false;">编辑摘要</a></span>
